5D82E1B9.Line1.FB4C3: Thank you. It may not look like much now, but this will help save someone’s limb.

F7775B3B.Line3.FB4C3: As for the smell, go to the tar pits. It won’t save your clothes, but maybe the odors will cancel each other out.

FB3FFC35.MenuLabel: “I have your gutweed. I’m never going to get this smell from these clothes.”
